  "text": "To design a novel antenna, the square antenna with a pair of rectangular sleeves, T-shaped slots and T-shaped conductor-backed plane is proposed. Based on the analysis of current distribution in UWB frequency band, it is observed that the currents at low frequency are distributed on the vertical plane at the monopole's bottom edge but the currents at high frequency are distributed on the horizontal plane [CITATION_1] . By cutting the T-shaped slots of suitable dimensions at the square radiating patch, it is found that much enhanced impedance bandwidth can be achieved for the proposed antenna.",
